      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver benchmarked against canonical flow problems; Gradation 1 required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "The solver has been benchmarked against the FDA nozzle and backward-facing step benchmark problems with results consistent with published literature. Order-of-accuracy tests confirm second-order spatial convergence for the momentum equations relevant to this COU."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
