      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments performed on the same device geometry and within the operating envelope of the COU.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments were performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry identical to the simulation geometry. Operating conditions span the full range of the five COU flow-speed combinations. Blood analog fluid properties are representative of clinical CPB conditions. The validation domain is sufficiently close to the COU to support the credibility claim."
    },
